<div class="title">Very Like Acid and Extremely Tranquil</div>
<div class="substance">2C-C & 2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Zantago&Exact=1">Zantago</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Zantago. "Very Like Acid and Extremely Tranquil: An Experience with 2C-C & 2C-I (exp31919)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 16, 2004. erowid.org/exp/31919</div>

